# AhmedETAP — Git Submodules Configuration
# =============================================================================
# This file explicitly declares that this repository has NO submodules.
# It exists to prevent Vercel build warnings:
#   "Warning: Failed to fetch one or more git submodules"
#
# Previous gitlink references (ETAP-AI-WORK, public-apis) were removed
# in commit 2485d7b. This file ensures git/Vercel knows there are no
# submodules to fetch.
